{"type": "article", "id": 11130, "title": "如大理石般的浴室家具", "description": "", "date": "2015-06-24T12:00:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 12, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235825TqLyKPMNhOu4xQbS.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t在今年的迈阿密巴塞尔设计展上，英国设计师 Max Lamb 向批量标准化生产的卫浴产品发出了挑战，他与材料设计工作室 Dzek 合作，设计了一套黑色大理石纹路与质感的卫浴家具产品，希望能够拓展人们对于浴室的体验与想象力，希望一改人们对船用浴室设计的刻板印象，尽量做到高效、实用并且节约空间。设计师希望这种如大理石一般的材料能够与不同的浴室环境相匹配，减少浴室中那些非必要的物件。\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052358228mv5r7uPwMkqBihW.jpg\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.78850856\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052358220k3UQaMeKLgXl5HE.jpg\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.76405868\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052358233RU8zyvbFfXnhZg4.jpg\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.9792176\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235823ZgyEIBj73HVOR8pt.jpg\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.75305623\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235824u8vi2LGmxCPajnlU.jpg\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.85696822\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235824QEtuMgc0zAwkC2HX.jpg\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.69682152\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n\t</p>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}